<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.232506>
    dc:description "FIGURES 7 − 12. Lachesilla huitoto n. sp. Male. 7. Forewing. 8. Hindwing. 9. Front view of head. 10. Paraprocts, epiproct and clunial apophysis. 11. Terminalia, lateral view. 12. Phallosome and claspers, ventral view. Scales in mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/232506/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.232508>
    dc:description "FIGURES 20 − 22. Lachesilla huitoto n. sp. Male and female variations. 20. Male forewing. 21. Female forewing. 22. Male clunial apophysis and epiproct. Scales in mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/232508/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.232507>
    dc:description "FIGURES 13 − 19. Lachesilla huitoto n. sp. Female. 13. Forewing. 14. Hindwing. 15. Front view of head. 16. Paraproct. 17. Subgenital plate. 18. Gonapophyses and ninth sternum. 19. Epiproct. Scales in mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/232507/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

